<h4><a href="https://www.yicai.com/news/100835399.html">腾讯发布 Q3 财报</a></h4>
<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1378829" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/tengx.jpg" alt="" width="3000" height="2000" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/tengx.jpg 3000w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/tengx-360x240.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/tengx-768x512.jpg 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/tengx-1024x683.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 3000px) 100vw, 3000px" /></p>
<p>《第一财经》消息，腾讯控股发布第三季度业绩报告。财报显示，公司第三季度营收达到了 1254.5 亿元，同比增长 29%，环比增长 9%；公司第三季度净利润 385.4 亿元，同比增 89%，环比增 16%。</p>
<p>微信及 Wechat 月活跃帐户 12.1 亿，同比增长 5.4%；QQ 的智能终端月活账户为 6.2 亿，同比则下降 5.5%。分大板块来看，游戏、金融科技以及广告几大业务板块均录得双位数的正增长。</p>
<h4>特斯拉成为全球工程学专业最具吸引力雇主</h4>
<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1378830" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/getty_1183832731_411127.jpg" alt="" width="1920" height="1080" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/getty_1183832731_411127.jpg 1920w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/getty_1183832731_411127-360x203.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/getty_1183832731_411127-768x432.jpg 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/getty_1183832731_411127-1024x576.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 1920px) 100vw, 1920px" /></p>
<p>智通财经消息，调查研究咨询公司 Universum 在新报告指出，特斯拉成为了全球工程专业学生认为最具吸引力的雇主。</p>
<p>于 2017-2019 年间，特斯拉均排名第二。今年，该公司首次超越 NASA 和 SpaceX 登上榜首。</p>
<h4><a href="https://tech.ifeng.com/c/81Kyt78zSbz">滴滴获得上海新增自动驾驶测试路段牌照</a></h4>
<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1378831" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/AE8CAAD8553D09F2BB0CD99815F73A0AF97C2D54_w832_h552.jpg" alt="" width="832" height="552" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/AE8CAAD8553D09F2BB0CD99815F73A0AF97C2D54_w832_h552.jpg 832w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/AE8CAAD8553D09F2BB0CD99815F73A0AF97C2D54_w832_h552-360x239.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/AE8CAAD8553D09F2BB0CD99815F73A0AF97C2D54_w832_h552-768x510.jpg 768w" sizes="(max-width: 832px) 100vw, 832px" /></p>
<p>凤凰网消息，滴滴自动驾驶宣布获得上海市新增自动驾驶测试路段牌照。官方表示，滴滴自动驾驶是首家获得上海三个测试区牌照的企业。</p>
<p>滴滴于 2016 年开展自动驾驶研发，研发团队规模 400 余人，2019 年 8 月，团队独立为滴滴子公司。</p>
<h3><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1357461" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/citylife.png" alt="" width="1029" height="153" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/citylife.png 1029w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/citylife-360x54.png 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/citylife-768x114.png 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/citylife-1024x152.png 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 1029px) 100vw, 1029px" /></h3>
<h4><a href="https://www.prnasia.com/story/298022-1.shtml">乐高盲文积木颗粒项目在中国盲校开启测试</a></h4>
<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1378832" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/1.jpeg" alt="" width="2700" height="1800" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/1.jpeg 2700w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/1-360x240.jpeg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/1-768x512.jpeg 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/1-1024x683.jpeg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 2700px) 100vw, 2700px" /></p>
<p>乐高携手中国盲文出版社，在中国开展乐高盲文积木颗粒项目的测试。目前，乐高在北京、上海、广州、泰安的四所盲校已经完成了对教师的相关培训，进入到课堂测试的阶段，预计所有的测试和评估工作将于今年年底前完成。</p>
<p>正在中国测试的拼音版乐高盲文积木颗粒是首个拉丁语系外的语言版本，包含 400 块积木，涵盖所有的汉语拼音字母、数字 0 到 9，还有常用的数字符号、音调符号等。</p>
<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1378833" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/image3.jpg" alt="" width="800" height="450" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/image3.jpg 800w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/image3-360x203.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/image3-768x432.jpg 768w" sizes="(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px" /></p>
<p>所有积木颗粒上的凸点能够与盲文字母一一对应，并与乐高玩乐系统完全兼容。健全儿童和成人也能够通过这套工具，与视障儿童一同玩乐。</p>
<h4><a href="https://www.jiemian.com/article/5261518.html">北京地铁未来安检和检票将合二为一</a></h4>
<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1378834" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/160517805735796600_a700x398.jpg" alt="" width="700" height="398" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/160517805735796600_a700x398.jpg 700w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/160517805735796600_a700x398-360x205.jpg 360w" sizes="(max-width: 700px) 100vw, 700px" /></p>
<p>界面消息，北京地铁运营公司副总工程师魏运表示，目前北京地铁正在研究将安检与检票环节「合二为一」的新型快速安检设备，乘客可以在通过安检的同时完成刷卡扫码，无需再次过闸机。</p>
<p>此外，北京地铁未来还推出基于乘客信用体系的「信用安检」，携带小包的乘客或可无需进行安检，直接进站乘车。「信用安检」去年起在北京地铁阜成门站试点，乘客可以通过亿通行 app 申请通行证。</p>
<h4><a href="https://cn.engadget.com/nike-jordan-11-adapt-072416307.html">耐克将推出自动绑鞋带版 Air Jordan XI</a></h4>
<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1378835" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/ef2131f0-24b6-11eb-a6fe-9c82b8df60e6.jpeg" alt="" width="960" height="636" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/ef2131f0-24b6-11eb-a6fe-9c82b8df60e6.jpeg 960w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/ef2131f0-24b6-11eb-a6fe-9c82b8df60e6-360x239.jpeg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/ef2131f0-24b6-11eb-a6fe-9c82b8df60e6-768x509.jpeg 768w" sizes="(max-width: 960px) 100vw, 960px" /></p>
<p>Engadget 消息，耐克将推出带有自动绑鞋带功能的 Air Jordan XI，中底部分配有可变色的灯光，用户可通过 app 来控制鞋身松紧和灯光。</p>
<p>耐克将于 12 月 30 日在 SNKRS 上架这个鞋款，价格暂未公布。</p>
<h4><a href="https://www.gamesradar.com/official-metapod-sleeping-bag-launches-in-japan/">万代推出「铁甲蛹」睡袋</a></h4>
<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1378836" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/premium-bandai-metapod-sleeping-bag-release-info-1.jpg" alt="" width="1800" height="1200" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/premium-bandai-metapod-sleeping-bag-release-info-1.jpg 1800w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/premium-bandai-metapod-sleeping-bag-release-info-1-360x240.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/premium-bandai-metapod-sleeping-bag-release-info-1-768x512.jpg 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/premium-bandai-metapod-sleeping-bag-release-info-1-1024x683.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 1800px) 100vw, 1800px" /></p>
<p>日本玩具品牌万代发布了一款以宝可梦「铁甲蛹」为主题的睡袋。这款睡袋只有 150cm 长，用户可能要坐着或侧躺才能舒服休息。</p>
<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1378837" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/pod.jpg" alt="" width="1300" height="884" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/pod.jpg 1300w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/pod-360x245.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/pod-768x522.jpg 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/pod-1024x696.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 1300px) 100vw, 1300px" /></p>
<p>「铁甲蛹」定价 3.5 万日元（约人民币 2230 元），目前预售已经开启，预计明年 4 月发售。</p>
<h3><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1293890" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/wangyo.png" alt="" width="1029" height="180" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/wangyo.png 1029w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/wangyo-360x63.png 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/wangyo-768x134.png 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/wangyo-1024x179.png 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 1029px) 100vw, 1029px" /></h3>
<h4><a href="https://weibo.com/1699432410/JtB9Vcy9X">快递员和育儿嫂也能评职称了</a></h4>
<p>人社部近日印发通知，支持企业自主开展技能人才评价、发放职业技能等级证书，同时建立健全职业技能等级认定与专业技术职称评审的贯通机制。</p>
<p>这意味着，快递员、育儿嫂等 1.7 亿技能劳动者，也能像医生、工程师等一样参加职称评定了。</p>
<p>网友：「有晋升制度才有更多人愿意去干，不管是主观选择也好，还是没得选也罢。」「快递员评职称，也能和职称相符的工资吗？」</p>
<h3><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1357583" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/fri.png" alt="" width="1029" height="153" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/fri.png 1029w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/fri-360x54.png 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/fri-768x114.png 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/fri-1024x152.png 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 1029px) 100vw, 1029px" /></h3>
<h4>一起看个展：《马克・夏加尔中国首展》</h4>
<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1378786" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/4979332403521728173.jpeg" alt="" width="724" height="1024" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/4979332403521728173.jpeg 724w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/4979332403521728173-360x509.jpeg 360w" sizes="(max-width: 724px) 100vw, 724px" /></p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><img src="https://s.w.org/images/core/emoji/11/72x72/1f4cd.png" alt="📍" class="wp-smiley" style="height: 1em; max-height: 1em;" /><strong>  中央美术学院美术馆廊坊馆·廊坊</strong></p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><strong><img src="https://s.w.org/images/core/emoji/11/72x72/231b.png" alt="⌛" class="wp-smiley" style="height: 1em; max-height: 1em;" />  2020.10.9 &#8211; 2021.1.18</strong></p>
<p style="text-align: left;">马克・夏加尔（1887-1985）是白俄罗斯裔法国画家、版画家和设计师。他历经立体派、超现实主义等现代艺术流派的实践与洗礼，发展出独特的个人绘画风格，在现代绘画史上占有重要的地位。</p>
<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1378788" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/poste.jpg" alt="" width="1500" height="1025" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/poste.jpg 1500w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/poste-360x246.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/poste-768x525.jpg 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/poste-1024x700.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 1500px) 100vw, 1500px" /></p>
<p>这次中国首展带来了 155 件作品，涵盖油画、水彩画、水粉画、坦培拉、蚀刻版画等艺术形式。</p>
<h4>本周上映</h4>
<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1378789" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/films.jpg" alt="" width="2000" height="558" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/films.jpg 2000w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/films-360x100.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/films-768x214.jpg 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/films-1024x286.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p>